Hello! The links I put it the previous message are to join the C Study Group Zoom calls. It’ll be the same link each month. They’re not the calendar invitations. I’ve been having a lot of trouble trying to get .ics files for the entire series (as opposed to just the Feb session). In any case, here are links to .ics files for February for each cohort: <https://us02web.zoom.us/meeting/tZIsdu6grjwpG9Y5cJjMmck8COoRaJ_EWYbk/ics?icsToken=DLUiMnsfivCKLSUn8AAALAAAALCUO1FAtskJQJVc7kmP9KwFXlW5XzNcsBBpKIP2Yke_t0eWjzwsGJCxq-vNChhpgfihAx4-7Y48Adc7qTAwMDAwMQ&meetingMasterEventId=ZSEjvS03ROa4K8SmZYtKGQ|cohort 1>, <https://us02web.zoom.us/meeting/tZUqcOqtrD4pHdAvSNtUchupobP162j18MyS/ics?icsToken=DFzxJ2fwKSEnPYUITAAALAAAAAFC9jKIk78jzn2VJ0anoMZqwJnkwKroKbxKLzAe4k165-7w_BTk64NjfW30nKWIoBdkBF6eFV5F0zA1mzAwMDAwMQ&meetingMasterEventId=3yx8AScaSuCaz9WSrMCNQg|cohort 2>, <https://us02web.zoom.us/meeting/tZItdeygrzsqG9ZwupEgseR0eYwmDFlMGTDK/ics?icsToken=DDwhWyeEbhHIDMjZXwAALAAAAPxVDVJd5Q3SPhGh0Esu6z77gcuvPIEDWt5HBBcLeZHW_t1wHoyCBUOx6pY94lG_9U6dk5Yirnnu9v1_PzAwMDAwMQ&meetingMasterEventId=oqxjeVVHSr2mm7BxNh1LZQ|cohort 3>. I’ll put links for .ics files for subsequent months into this channel at the beginning of each month.

If you use Google Calendar, you can get all the sessions at once <https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/1?cid=ab59b5988cef70d576d045f33a7b4ec633d665afb070aaf696b4b353254c74dc@group.calendar.google.com|using this link>. This will give you all three cohorts, though, so you’ll need to delete the sessions not applicable to you.
